msg: If an unknown Content-* header is received for a PUT request, we must not
ignore it but reply with 501 per RFC 2616 9.6.

author: rpluem
msg: If a malformed Content-Range header is received for a PUT request, we
must not use the supplied content per RFC 2616 14.16. Send 400 response
